    Ritual
By: Sri Ramakrishna
---
When a flood comes from the ocean, all the land is deep under water.
Before the flood, the boat could have reached the ocean only by
following the winding course of the river. But after the flood, one
can row straight to the ocean. One need not take a roundabout course.
